{"tid":1022052,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"不得不承認，韓風末落，而家興既係中國風","createTime":"2019-02-14T16:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T01:29:30.000Z","uid":34934,"like":9,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c3787799eb3a053ba8257f94f0eee93bd2b27f33","tid":1022052,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:39:30.000Z","msg":"大陸妹比韓國妹天然，素質又好，又pure，韓妹個樣膠到，相比之下兩回事。<br />\n你見好多香港人都北上搵大陸妹、藝人好多都搵大陸妹就知。<br />\n<br />\n講歌中國風既歌越嚟越紅，e.g.莊心妍，相比韓國歌已經唔hit<br />\n<br />\n拍劇方面，中國古代劇出名就知，延禧已經係好例子，仲未計之前小美好個啲，拍落去真係好好睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_9RrEYK6dcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_9RrEYK6dcs&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPafwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=3961b73d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_9RrEYK6dcs</a><br />\n<br />\n見到中國文化開始係亞洲有領導地位，突然有啲自豪光榮感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a2509ab2e2db04388c05e9537a1abb2018942c","tid":1022052,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"大家點睇"},{"pid":"45020c50df95e06acd3452cc9919cb40c7fa05c9","tid":1022052,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513ee05a04795f072e93de4ea55a60944fb34508","tid":1022052,"uid":15886,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫中風"},{"pid":"73e8c00423ce5a502fa18b34441e529a06eb85c2","tid":1022052,"uid":8377,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"513ee05a04795f072e93de4ea55a60944fb34508","tid":1022052,"uid":15886,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫中風"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:49:34.000Z","msg":"點解台灣風唔叫台風"},{"pid":"bcdf2e6a4ddfe8a685d89784d58db223cc1504ec","tid":1022052,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:50:42